looking at lots of books in here.

265
00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:52.470
Yeah.

266
00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:57.970
The question is why did
Michiko-san touch that book?

267
00:16:05.800 --> 00:16:07.190
What's this scratch?

268
00:16:14.210 --> 00:16:15.600
This is blood.

269
00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:20.440
