295
00:17:42.970 --> 00:17:45.460
Why did you do that?

296
00:17:45.770 --> 00:17:47.920
Something caught my attention.

297
00:17:47.920 --> 00:17:50.210
I cut my finger when I did, though.

298
00:17:51.190 --> 00:17:54.170
Was the thing that caught your attention...?

299
00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:57.270
Ah, this is it.

300
00:17:57.820 --> 00:17:59.840
I've been looking for this book.

301
00:18:00.130 --> 00:18:02.600
How considerate of you.

302
00:18:03.990 --> 00:18:04.850
Damn it.

303
00:18:06.280 --> 00:18:08.490
I cut myself on the paper.

304
00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:09.950
