324
00:19:14.630 --> 00:19:15.820
You're wrong.

325
00:19:15.820 --> 00:19:16.550
What?

326
00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:20.930
You were Omura-san's only target.

327
00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:26.930
Michiko-san had the bad luck of
falling for Omura-san's trap.

328
00:19:27.080 --> 00:19:32.060
How did he plan to make me
pick up the poisoned book?

329
00:19:32.910 --> 00:19:35.720
Probably by doing this.

330
00:19:36.690 --> 00:19:40.070
