340
00:20:18.920 --> 00:20:22.990
But Nagisa-san could've
fallen for that trap, too.

341
00:20:23.340 --> 00:20:25.740
That's why he used a German book.

342
00:20:25.910 --> 00:20:29.810
Even if Nagisa-san can't read German,

343
00:20:29.810 --> 00:20:32.500
she'd at least notice if
a book were upside down.

344
00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.250
There are books from all
over the world here, right?

345
