357
00:21:04.350 --> 00:21:07.400
I've always supported you.

358
00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:08.280
Supported me?

359
00:21:08.730 --> 00:21:10.000
Don't be absurd!

360
00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:13.200
You've worked me like a dog!

361
00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:17.960
I'm sorry for stealing your books
and selling them when I was broke.

362
00:21:18.250 --> 00:21:22.880
But you worked me like
a slave because of that!

363
00:21:26.460 --> 00:21:29.140
I had reached my limit.

364
